snippet.title: Link: The Faces of Evil (Zelda CD-I) - Part 1
snippet.description:
Well, here I am playing one third of the Unholy Triforce. We see a tutorial, the infamous intro, farming for snowballs, and getting the power sword. And much ado about doing the duck walk.

Was originally recorded for BrainscratchComms for their 5th Anniversary. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8nJtU6Ifgak&list=PLuwOO7jn4Z5KZgNlaWRPYzHHDB32qA827
